  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to analyze the correlation between intra-abdominal view and
      patient recovery in secondary peritonitis, and to create a new classification based on these
      results. Additionally, a variety of inflammatory markers from blood samples will be collected
      in order to analyze their correlation with patient outcomes.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
